Executive Summary & Problems That Occurred 3





Troubles that occurred during the project:
1. We experienced a problem where all the ODS Dictionary tables were populating Duplicated Data. We created a CTE that we used to remove the duplicate data and the issue was fixed.
2. We also encountered an issue where the Fact table Date key kept on Populating Null Values. We went back one step and created a new stored procedure that we used to populate the Dim Calendar table and then we populated the fact table and the issue was fixed.




How to avoid Problems when Building a Data warehouse.
